  "title": "Sales Executive - Freight Forwarding",
  "description": "<p>• Identify and prospect new business/clients via sales/cold-calling and sales activities.</p><p>• Generate new sales leads, contract negotiation and sales closure.</p><p>• Responsible for delivering expected sales revenue target and profitability.</p><p>• Attend to customers feedback/ complaints and follow up with high-quality after sales services.</p><p>• Act as the customers' main point of contact, by liaising closely with the relevant departments to ensure that their queries, problems, or issues are deal with appropriately.</p><p><br /></p><p>Benefit : </p><p><br /></p><p>Basic salary + very attractive commission scheme </p><p>Up to 20 days of leave to start</p><p>5 days work</p><p>Medical benefits</p><p>Handphone allowance </p><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume to : Edmund.tan@tscsin.com</p>",
